From the editor's note in the back of the book:

NOTE: The RADICAL DREAMER series that ran in the old Hero Illustrated magazine takes place, chronologically, on story page 26 of this issue. You don't need to have read it to enjoy DREAMS CANNOT DIE!, but it does serve to add some detail to RAD's activities on the DreamNet. The HERO series was cut short by that magazine's cancellation, but the story will be completed and incorporated into the special RADICAL DREAMER PRIME, due out in April.
